data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bath residence boasts 3,238 square feet of living space, set against the serene backdrop of a tranquil pond on a sprawling 1.84-acre lot, which will be enjoyed from your covered back porch, complete with an outdoor kitchen. Step inside to discover a spacious, light-filled living area that seamlessly flows past your formal dining room into the spacious open plan.  Cooking enthusiasts will adore the large island kitchen with a walk-in pantry and a butler's work area, perfect for hosting gatherings.  Boasting a large media room, and a small bonus area that can be home to a work space and a 3-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and storage.
